<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>InnoMotech - Bientôt Disponible</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #000 0%, #1a1a1a 100%);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in;
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            color: #888;
            animation: slideUp 1.5s ease-out;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .coming-soon {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #0071e3;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { 
                transform: translateY(30px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }
            .tagline {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            .tagline {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .tagline {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .coming-soon {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>InnoMotech</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Une nouvelle génération de boîtiers innovants, actuellement en phase de développement et en cours de brevetabilité. Notre technologie redéfinira vos attentes.</p>
        <p class="coming-soon">Bientôt disponible</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
